para sa Pill-Tasting Competition?

756
00:34:13,000 --> 00:34:14,929
Ang aking amo ay si Xin Xiong. Ako si Xin Mei.

757
00:34:15,770 --> 00:34:17,870
[Wang Yanqing
ng pamilya Wang ng Jinqiu]

758
00:34:17,110 --> 00:34:18,710
Sabay na tayong umakyat.

759
00:34:26,400 --> 00:34:27,800
Anong problema, Miss?

760
00:34:28,360 --> 00:34:29,230
Maaari ba akong magtanong, sir,

761
00:34:29,480 --> 00:34:30,880
