762
00:34:31,280 --> 00:34:31,880
Anong bangka?

763
00:34:32,510 --> 00:34:34,030
Ang bangkang tatawid sa ilog.

764
00:34:34,030 --> 00:34:34,889
Bakit sumakay ng bangka?

765
00:34:36,070 --> 00:34:38,600
Paano ka pa tumawid sa ilog
walang bangka?

766
00:34:38,800 --> 00:34:39,800
May tulay.

767
00:34:40,190 --> 00:34:41,190
may tulay ba?

768
00:34:43,800 --> 00:34:44,800
May tulay?

769
00:34:57,880 --> 00:34:58,400
Lu,

770
00:34:59,230 --> 00:35:00,690
nung dumating kami kanina,

771
00:35:00,770 --> 00:35:01,920
Nakita ko ang maraming imortal na sekta

772
00:35:01,920 --> 00:35:02,820
darating para lumahok sa paparating na

773
00:35:02,820 --> 00:35:04,070
Kumpetisyon sa Pagtikim ng Pill.

774
00:35:04,070 --> 00:35:04,730
Sa tingin mo

775
00:35:04,950 --> 00:35:06,810
Baka dumating din si Immortal Xin?

776
00:35:12,440 --> 00:35:13,800
Sa kanyang limitadong kakayahan,

777
00:35:13,800 --> 00:35:15,130
hindi siya dapat ipadala sa

778
00:35:15,230 --> 00:35:17,490
makilahok sa naturang mahalagang kaganapan.

779
00:35:17,760 --> 00:35:19,290
Sa karakter ni Su Taiyi,

780
00:35:19,890 --> 00:35:20,590
