784
00:35:47,220 --> 00:35:49,920
[Sa mapanglaw na kawalan]

785
00:35:50,090 --> 00:35:53,150
[Saan maaaring maghanap ng imortalidad?]

786
00:35:53,480 --> 00:35:56,550
[Pagpapagaling sa Mundo]

787
