[Zhi Bocheng,
Transit Commissioner ng Jingzhou]

790
00:36:11,910 --> 00:36:14,300
[Master Fu ng Qingshan Sect]

791
00:36:14,370 --> 00:36:16,370
[Longevity Hall]

792
00:36:34,670 --> 00:36:36,320
Nasaan ang mga taga-Tianyuan Sect
Solar at Lunar Cavern

793
00:36:36,320 --> 00:36:37,550
