794
00:36:37,920 --> 00:36:39,030
Master Gongyu mula sa
ang Solar at Lunar Cavern

795
00:36:39,030 --> 00:36:40,510
ay papunta na.

796
00:36:41,230 --> 00:36:43,290
I-activate niya ang formation mamaya

797
00:36:43,920 --> 00:36:45,450
