820
00:37:28,030 --> 00:37:29,670
Hindi mo alam ito o iyon.

821
00:37:30,070 --> 00:37:31,800
Saka bakit mo kami pinatawag dito?

822
00:37:32,470 --> 00:37:34,070
Tinipon ko kayong lahat dito ngayon

823
00:37:34,200 --> 00:37:35,160
