856
00:39:56,960 --> 00:39:57,630
Sino siya?

857
00:39:59,330 --> 00:40:01,480
Master Gongyu
ng Solar at Lunar Cavern.

858
00:40:01,480 --> 00:40:02,540
Masama ang ugali niya.

859
00:40:05,890 --> 00:40:07,960
Nandito ang lahat para gamitin
ang Gongshan Jade Tablet

860
