863
00:40:15,360 --> 00:40:16,230
Hindi eksakto.

864
00:40:16,840 --> 00:40:18,510
Noon,
ang Labindalawang Imortal na Sekta ay ganap na suportado

865
00:40:18,510 --> 00:40:20,280
Divine Physician Su
sa pagtatatag ng Chongling Valley,

866
00:40:20,280 --> 00:40:22,440
